metadata.name: Fractional Uprising Studios Membership #1
metadata.description: Fractional Uprising Studios is creating 1/1 community content creations through a process called 'Reverse Production'. This NFT represents 'OPENSEASON', the studios premiere NFT battle royale and acts as a membership needed to play the game and join the community. Join the [Discord](https://fustudios.chat/) to start your experience.
